rows.label: tlk41400021_03_msg0001
rows.name:
From what I hear, there's an incredible
sculptor living in Invidia!

rows.label: tlk41400021_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Apparently he creates the most
wonderful sculptures of Queen Lagert.
Nothing like them in all of Alst!

rows.label: tlk41400021_03_msg0003
rows.name:
Someday, I want to see what a
sculptor as fine as that could do
with Gulan wood.

rows.label: tlk41400021_03_msg0004
rows.name:
Perhaps if we strengthen our
trade links with Invidia, it could
happen eventually...

rows.label: tlk41400021_03_msg0005
rows.name:
I can almost picture it now...
The Wood-Carven Queen!
Ah, what a sight it would be.
